<lb n="1052b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1052b1501" style="margin-left:1em">右上三部三卷。<cb:jl_byline>大興善寺三藏不空譯</cb:jl_byline><note place="inline">重標於此</note>。</p></item></list></cb:div>
